SimpleNotepad
-------------

SimpleNotepad is minimalistic notepad for the Android system.
Lack of candy animations/graphic makes it fast and lightweight.

SimpleNotepad is licensed under the terms of 2-clause BSD Licence.



Works on
--------

It has been tested on:
 - Samsung Galaxy 3 (i5800) on Android 2.2 (XWJPF)
 - Android emulator on Android 2.1-update1


Known issues
------------
 - ContextMenu works only on notes with URL text


